{"tid":674870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：踢跌阿婆　大番薯遭正義哥生擒","createTime":"2018-05-23T05:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T05:37:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"96e867703fbc37c10a9968b4da5bde03b258f351","tid":674870,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180523/20398994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180523%2F20398994&d=S1Ywlxr8tDy42Wc%2BRmdRtwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5d6709d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180523%2F20398994&h=8d6b35f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180523/20398994</a><br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：踢跌阿婆　大番薯遭正義哥生擒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180523/large/a1404a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180523%2Flarge%2Fa1404a.gif&h=a1e46bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■正義哥睇唔過眼，將大番薯一嘢壓落地。讀者梁小姐提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果話打女人嘅係賤男，咁打阿婆就係賤中賤！話說噚日下晝3點幾，讀者梁小姐見到身形似大番薯嘅男人，搭輕鐵去到元朗豐年路，同佢一齊落車嘅仲有一位婆婆，呢個時候大番薯起腳踢向婆婆，婆婆當場跌低，坐咗喺月台。<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界仲係有好多真漢子嘅，一名哥哥仔睇唔過眼，一嘢就將大番薯壓落地下。梁小姐當時啱啱經過車站，聽到有人叫「做乜撳住我！」而坐喺旁邊嘅婆婆就摸住隻腳，睇表情應該好痛喇，過咗接近10分鐘，終於有市民行去一街之隔嘅元朗警署通知警察，「警察好快嚟到，6個差人圍住佢，佢仲好輕佻咁鬧人，都唔驚」。最後警員以手銬鎖起大番薯，將佢帶署調查，而婆婆就由救護車送院。<br />\n<br />\n據講大番薯同阿婆三唔識七，雙方之前又冇碰撞過，大番薯點解要踢阿婆，要警察查吓至知，但係小記認為，無論如何，淨係識蝦阿婆，算咩男人呀！  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n屬政府財物　可判囚10年<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：的士佬H＆R　網民一粒鐘緝兇"},{"pid":"7caa1727e8063b81a96db46a9855d97930deb930","tid":674870,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98ab265e01bc1c6b9fc5711c56b2f468f4e547c8","tid":674870,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"正義哥應該係老趙嚟"},{"pid":"e7823f33451a0fe986d05e930294fa0bba45e606","tid":674870,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁就報警？元朗不嬲freestyle。冇咩事都唔好入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢度ok既<br />\n係怕內街d南亞同公仔佬啫"},{"pid":"4fca85748452ce78800e7cf331ff7a630b8e9f87","tid":674870,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"壓住人嗰個似大番薯多啲"},{"pid":"26db0bf28adbe0fe51fb3c4fadf60cc7b045fbc4","tid":674870,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7823f33451a0fe986d05e930294fa0bba45e606","tid":674870,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁就報警？元朗不嬲freestyle。冇咩事都唔好入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢度ok既<br />\n係怕內街d南亞同公仔佬啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"內街係搞咁多次光復行動裏面最刺激一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛屎佬基本上三對一圍我哋 後來大隊到先至甩身<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/133723_2fc1d290de9ec2aec68c53dbaf1a8332.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F133723_2fc1d290de9ec2aec68c53dbaf1a8332.png&h=92b8d72c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b26d8b7a980b6caf1160a06b775ab0e208676881","tid":674870,"uid":9564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"後面條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16b6ac874d6d6233b54397740866cb037280ef8","tid":674870,"uid":157498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"一睇就知個廢佬趕住落車撞到人，跟本就係撩交打，好撞唔撞，撞到個傻佬"}]}